hard to count on.

00:16:34.380 --> 00:16:37.060
Like your boss comes up to you: "What are
you're doing". "Oh I'm just waiting for the

00:16:37.060 --> 00:16:40.389
big flash. Don't worry". Or "I'm gonna go
home and take a nap."

00:16:40.389 --> 00:16:44.930
So, getting used to having lots of ideas and
then going back and choosing is a better way,

00:16:44.930 --> 00:16:49.890
I think, to be innovative. It's just like
-- have a part of the day that's very generative,

00:16:49.890 --> 00:16:54.760
and then a part where you can judge. But get
comfortable with lots of ideas.

00:16:54.760 --> 00:16:59.200
