00:17:04.490 --> 00:17:08.029
five that were actually new or different.
The next 20 produced nothing but laughter.

00:17:08.029 --> 00:17:12.959
And ideas 80 through 100 produced 10 that
were amazing. Thankfully, we didn't give up

00:17:12.959 --> 00:17:17.549
when the well ran dry around idea number 60."-from
"The Ebb and Flow of Ideas", of Dev Patnaik

00:17:17.549 --> 00:17:20.100
who is the founder of Jump, neat guy.

00:17:20.100 --> 00:17:24.629
