in the doorframe, bounced up and down, and

00:26:41.229 --> 00:26:45.599
we made it free-standing. The problem with
the one in the doorframe is, moms loved it

00:26:45.599 --> 00:26:48.480
and hated it. They loved it because the infant
loved it. They hated it 'cause they thought

00:26:48.480 --> 00:26:53.909
it might fall down. It's dangerous. Or if
you live in a small apartment building, it

00:26:53.909 --> 00:26:55.190
blocked your key passageway.

00:26:55.190 --> 00:26:59.759
So we made it free-standing. And we could
quickly--we took that insight, quickly prototyped

00:26:59.759 --> 00:27:01.239
it up 'cause we had all this junk around.

00:27:01.239 --> 00:27:06.749
