00:30:07.049 --> 00:30:09.889
So a few closing thoughts.

00:30:09.889 --> 00:30:14.669
Don't take yourself too seriously, discover
the opposite of play isn't work. This is sort

00:30:14.669 --> 00:30:19.379
of the whole class is based around the opposite
of play isn't work. It's, I think, boredom,

00:30:19.379 --> 00:30:21.169
or in the worst cases, depression.

00:30:21.169 --> 00:30:24.519
So if you're not interested or passionate
about what you're doing, you're not gonna

00:30:24.519 --> 00:30:31.570
innovate. So, most people think play is for
kids. It's frivolous. I think that's totally

00:30:31.570 --> 00:30:32.570
wrong.

00:30:32.570 --> 00:30:36.720
I think as you get older you should be incredibly
excited about what you're doing. If people

00:30:36.720 --> 00:30:41.730
