about this way about their hobbies. Like some

00:30:41.730 --> 00:30:45.749
of their hobbies are incredible amount of
effort, "work" so to speak. But they love

00:30:45.749 --> 00:30:49.289
doing it, so they want to keep doing it more
and more.

00:30:49.289 --> 00:30:52.650
So I think for innovation, if you can feel
the sort of playful mode, not maybe all of

00:30:52.650 --> 00:30:56.230
