The first is to realize when you're in a divergent

00:32:38.200 --> 00:32:41.789
mode, when you're creating ideas, and when
you're in a convergent mode and you're eliminating

00:32:41.789 --> 00:32:42.789
ideas.

00:32:42.789 --> 00:32:48.300
Too often, folks are somewhere in the middle
where they'll keep trying to come up with

00:32:48.300 --> 00:32:51.049
