quickly quickly take a group vote as to which

00:33:07.839 --> 00:33:12.379
ones. And that's just to sort of see where
the butterflies sort of land, and that will

00:33:12.379 --> 00:33:14.349
help sort of narrow some things.

00:33:14.349 --> 00:33:19.190
